    "body" : "<p>Try this</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;String&gt; StringarrayList = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;(); \n    FileWriter writer = new FileWriter(\"output.txt\", true); \n    for(String str: StringarrayList ) {\n      writer.write(str + \"\\n\");\n    }\n    writer.close();\n</code></pre>\n"
